  KEY INSIGHT: QR tournament has Q_k = (p-1)/4 for all k ≠ 0
  => ALL eigenspaces are IDENTICAL
  => Omega_m decomposes uniformly across eigenspaces
  => By THM-145, the per-eigenspace Omega profile is the same for all k
  => The total Omega_m = p * Omega_m(per eigenspace) + correction from k=0

